message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $17,500. It's a great deal for a product worth $15,000 to you. Let me know what you think!

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the product is worth $15,000 to me, so I would like to propose a price of $16,000 for the product. I hope this aligns better with your expectations. Looking forward to your response!
